systems sound sirens but are severely voicechallenged lrad mass notification systems broadcast warning sirens and highly intelligible messages to communicate to affected populations with one voice® during emergency situations learn more filling the critical gap between initial engagement  escalation of force as part of a layered escalation of force eof strategy lrad systems are a safer alternative to kinetic force and provide defense personnel more time and distance to distinguish between security threats and innocent civilians learn more safely establish  maintain large standoff zones lrad systems protect vital infrastructure and provide homeland security agencies an essential communications capability during regional and national emergencies learn more securing borders safely  remotely remotely operated lradrx® systems integrated with radar cameras and other sensors provide a critical first response capability and automated border security learn more protecting ships ports passengers  crew lrad systems extend standoff zones around ships  maritime facilities enhancing security and protecting personnel and assets learn more humanely  safely protecting wildlife  assets lrad systems broadcast a near infinite variety of tones and predator calls to safely deter wildlife at distances in excess of  meters and ensure against habituation learn more communicate anytime anywhere with lrad one voice® mobile mass notification public address  emergency communication for large events and extreme situations learn more the global leader in acoustic hailing devices learn more long range acoustic device® mass notification  pa systems remotely operated lrad® systems applications lrad is a game changer for communication introducing the lrad xl the lightest loudest ahd for its weight and size learn more lrad systems lineup lrad systems are powered by the company’s proprietary optimized driver and waveguide technology learn more long range communication lrads highly intelligible long ran