 generous donation equips our mobile clinics with versatile public address systems to better reach the communities we serve in malawi” for more information about the lrad x and its use by gaiaetaf please click humanitarian communication ride across america retired marine sgt toran gaal’s june – august  ride across america benefited the semper fi fund ret sgt gaal lost both his legs above his knee and hip and suffered a brain injury in an ied explosion june  in afghanistan his continuing mission is to raise awareness and educate people on the lives of those who are wounded and injured while serving in the us military read more about ret sgt gaal and his mile ride across america httpwwwtorangaalcom for more information on the semper fi fund visit httpssemperfifundorg domestic incidents during and after events such as hurricane katrina the landslides in oso wa and flooding in boulder co – the company responded by lending lrad systems to law enforcement and the national guard to communicate rescue instructions to stranded survivors and to provide information on relief and humanitarian assistance to people on the ground read the colorado national guard ‘thank you’ letter  polinsky children’s center pcc the ab and jessie polinsky children’s center pcc is the emergency shelter for children in san diego county pcc provides services to children who have been physically sexually and or emotionally abused medically or physically neglected andor have no parent or guardian the company and its employees participate generously in the annual toy drive to benefit pcc and children in need for more information visit httppromiseskidsorg holes for heroes® holes for heroes presents military appreciation events for the purpose of saluting thanking and supporting wounded and recovering military heroes frontlined based troops children and families of deployed troops and kias and recovering veterans in  the company’s sponsorship at the holes for heroes annual golf tournament served as a catalyst for a donation and future assistance to the support the enlisted project step step provides emergency financial and transition assistance grants to active duty and recently discharged enlisted military members and their families for more information visit httpwwwstepsocalorg about lrad corporationtechnology  safety fact sheet trademark  copyright lrad in the news video library industry memberships strategic partnerships corporate citizenship privacy policy lrad xt mobile mass notification rapidly deployable highly intelligible voice  warning tone broadcasts with perfect ° coverage learn more grants  funding lrad corporation assists with the preparation of grant requests for federal state or local agencies learn more lrad product guide download download now lrad corporation in the news the global leader in long range acoustic hailing devices request a quote support lrad in the news filter by years all           sy hideaway using lrad to deter maritime threats courtesy of dockwalk “three days into the passage passing close to land sy hideaway’s mate spotted two boats on the horizon approaching just after dawn having alerted the security team member on watch hideaway’s antipiracy plan was put into action broadcasting on vhf channel  and using the lrad the captain warned the approaching skiffs to stay back having seemingly decided the sy hideaway was not the soft target they first appeared to be the boats broke away not to be seen again”   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   lrad deployed to disperse unruly campus concert crowd in maryland courtesy of delmarvanowcom “chief tim bozman of princess anne police department also confirmed that his agency responded to the scene to help with dispersing the crowd bozman said officers from his department were requested by state police to deploy its lrad system a portable speaker officers can use to communicate with crowds “its a very good piece of equipment for incidents like this” bozman said”   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   warning at sea be prepared be ready courtesy of eurasia review “over the years technology advances and user needs have resulted in the development of more effective equipment like long range acoustic devices lrad that direct sound from greater ranges towards the threat”   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   columbus oh police department demonstrates lrad xl courtesy of wcmhtv columbus oh columbus police unveiled a new hightech audio device which they plan to use for crowd control the lrad or long range acoustic device has the ability to clearly broadcast messages with a range of  miles the device can be used by swat for barricaded suspects or to communicate with citizens in the event of an emergency but it’s most likely use will be to communicate with crowds   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   lrad wins two platinum ast homeland security awards courtesy of american security today the lrad x and the lrad x have been honored by american security today ast with platinum awards respectively as ‘best mass notification system’ and ‘best long range acoustic hailing system’   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   lrad® corporation receives “best acoustic hailing service” award from government security news category communications solutions best acoustic hailing service – winner lrad corporation lrad rxl best mass notification system – finalist lrad corporation lrad ds read more government security news announces winners of  airport seaport border security awards   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   lrad x systems on board rpb  offshore patrol boats courtesy of naval technologycom rpb  coastal patrol boats are designed to enhance the maritime surveillance capabilities of naval forces the lrad xequipped boats are in service in the navies of west african countries senegal togo and ivory coast   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   singapore navy launches second lrad rx equipped littoral marine vessel courtesy of navaltodaycom the lmv’s represent a considerable increase in capability they are able to operate naval helicopters which our patrol vessels today are unable to do they can operate uavs unmanned aerial vehicles as well…and have the long range acoustic device and water cannons to deal with…maritime threats that the lmvs may encounter   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   southlake tx utilizes portable mass notification featuring lrad xm systems for outdoor events courtesy of mysouthlakenewscom the sirens lrad can act as loud speakers and are capable of providing eventspecific warnings and information to large crowds the sirens add an additional layer to our existing comprehensive warning capabilities they allow us to provide focused voicespecific warnings at the many special events that southlake hosts throughout the year   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………   houston tx rodeo deploys lrad xt for mass notification courtesy of the houston chronicle “we use it lrad to warn people should we have an emergency or an extreme weather event” – dan cheney vice president of the houston livestock and rodeo   …………………………………………………………………………………………………………………… ……………………………………………………………………………………………………………………    of »last » about lrad corporationtechnology  safety fact sheet trademark  copyright lrad in the news video library industry memberships strategic partnerships corporate citizenship privacy policy grants  funding lrad corporation assists with the preparation of grant requests for federal state or local agencies learn more lrad product guide downlo