other emergency notification measures are only effective if directories are continually updated lrad one voice® revolutionary lrad one voice systems are advanced mass notification solutions that broadcast warning sirens and exceptionally intelligible voice messages to protect and save lives lrad one voice systems ensure emergency warnings and general announcements are clearly heard and understood throughout coverage areas lrad life safety systems warn and communicate critical information to populations not receiving automated phone calls and other emergency notification measures by broadcasting attentioncommanding warning sirens and extraordinarily clear voice messages over wind traffic and background noise up to  sq kilometers from a single installation advanced technology optimized to the primary human hearing range of  –  khz lrad features advanced driver and waveguide technology to focus broadcasts in a ° pattern or transmit ° with uniform area coverage by maintaining a smooth frequency response with an intensity variation of less than db lrad has overcome the limitations of competitor systems by preventing audio fading and producing clear unambiguous communication across all broadcast frequencies lrad one voice systems are the only mass notification solutions that offer several volume control settings to customize broadcast area coverage remotely monitored and activated by tcpip fiber satellite wifi digital or analog radio ethernet or hard wire lrad one voice systems are the most flexible and easily configured mass notification solutions available superior voice intelligibility based on federal emergency management agency fema and us military united facilities criteria ufc guidelines the minimum standard for highpowered speaker array hpsa mass notification systems is a  speech transmission index sti measurement lrad one voice systems feature the highest sti rating in the mass notification industry at  substantially exceeding all fema and ufc voice intelligibility requirements lrad systems are selfcontained or easily integrated with existing communications infrastructure from portable devices to larger systems temporarily or permanently mounted on poles buildings trailers vehicles or helicopters lrad systems are highly effective in communicating lifesaving information locally and over large areas before during and in the aftermath of disasters and emergency situations inquire about financing options  related products lrad x learn more lrad x learn more lrad xl learn more lrad x learn more lrad rx learn more lrad rxl learn more lrad rx learn more lrad x mmt learn more lrad xi learn more lrad xl learn more lrad x learn more lrad xm learn more lrad xlmid learn more lrad x learn more lrad xl learn more lrad xt learn more lrad dsx learn more lrad dsxl learn more lrad ss learn more lrad ss learn more lrad ss learn more lrad soundsaberx learn more applicationsmass notification  emergency warning proven performance recreation areas  parks military mass notification  pa industrial facilities emergency communication first responders campus pa  emergency notification severe weather  tsunamis municipal  county emergency warning humanitarian response  relief acoustic design  modeling outdoor pa  emergency notification defense proven performance convoy protection checkpoints exclusion zones active shooter fob  perimeter security maritime proven performance navy  coast guard security  response exclusion zones oil  gas platforms law enforcement proven performance elevated risk first responders large event communication campus security correctional facilities firing range communication homeland security critical infrastructure evacuation  shelter perimeter security  first response community preparedness incident management emergency communication cbrn  hazmat incidents fire rescue border security air mobile perimeter security  response borstar virtual acoustic fence bortac preserving wildlife  protecting assets proven performance airports 