ibrary request a demo purchase request a quote where to purchase lrad rxl  lrad corporation the global leader in long range acoustic hailing devices request a quote support lrad rxl compact form factor exceptional performance lrad rxl remotely operated security  response system engineered and designed on a new proprietary pan and tilt system the lrad rxl is a lighter more compact version of the successful lrad rx system designed for integrated applications ranging from small vessels to fixed installation security solutions the lrad rxl can be controlled remotely across an ip network enabling system operators to create a fully functional unmanned perimeter security solution and respond to potential threats from a safe location the lrad rxl achieves a maximum peak output of db and broadcasts highly intelligible voice messages and warning tones from close range up to  meters featuring an integrated hd camera a highintensity  million candlepower searchlight optional and a robust ipaddressable full pan and tilt drive for precise aiming and tracking the lrad rxl can also be integrated with radar to provide automated intruder alerts the lrad rxl reduces manpower false alarms and deadly incidents while providing a highly effective and cost efficient remote response security solution the lrad rxl accepts motion commands from the lrad controller software through a point and click interface simply click on a target and the rx will move to center its acoustic broadcast onto a target a standard usb joystick not included can also be used to control the rxl’s motion lrad’s easy to use controller interface enables operators to visually identify a potential threat on the live video feed aim the lrad and deliver a powerful warning message or deterrent tone from the safety of a command and control center the lrad rxl’s ability to immediately interact with a potential threat remotely provides security personnel additional time and distance to accurately assess situations and scale their response appropriately features remotely control all functions through tcpip connection remotely respond to threats from a safe location low power requirements allweather use fixed infrastructure easy to use – increased coverage with single operator increased security coverage improved operational efficiency increased response capabilities safer alternative to nonlethal deterrent measures directionality power efficiency  range highly intelligible communication up to  meters safely communicates beyond standoff distances clear long range directional communication when integrated with radar creates a fully functional automated perimeter presence images  videos  lrad rxl images  videos specifications  lrad rxl specifications download the lrad rxl specifications datasheet here request a demo view all lrad products lrad x lrad x lrad xl lrad x lrad rx lrad rxl lrad rx lrad x mmt lrad  lrad xi lrad xl lrad x lrad xm lrad xlmid lrad x lrad xl lrad xt lrad dsx lrad dsxl lrad ss lrad ss lrad ss lrad soundsaberx lrad rxl applications law enforcement  defense  mass notification  homeland security  border security  maritime  wildlife  asset protection  learn more download datasheet downloads library request a demo purchase request a quote where to buy lrad rxl  lrad corporation the global leader in long range acoustic hailing devices request a quote support lrad rxl compact form factor exceptional performance lrad rxl remotely operated security  response system engineered and designed on a new proprietary pan and tilt system the lrad rxl is a lighter more compact version of the successful lrad rx system designed for integrated applications ranging from small vessels to fixed installation security solutions the lrad rxl can be controlled remotely across an ip network enabling system operators to create a fully functional unmanned perimeter security solution and respond to potential threats from a safe location the lrad rxl achieves a maximum peak output of db and broadcasts hig