arity and intelligibility featured in all lrad systems the lrad dsxl incorporates lrads xl driver technology which generates greater audio output for up to  more mass notification area coveragewe are expanding our mass notification product line to offer more broadcast area coverage and price options for our growing customer base commented richard s danforth chief executive officer of lrad corporation with scalable area coverage and ease of configuration and installation the lrad dsx and lrad dsxl provide highly intelligible cost effective public address and emergency communication for campuses industrial plants military bases and other large complexesthe lrad dsx has a meter range this rugged acoustic horn system is efficient low power and built for permanent outdoor installation for more information please click on lrad dsxpowered by lrads proprietary xl driver technology the lrad dsxl has a meter range and the same form factor as the lrad dsx when configured in a ° ring array the broadcast coverage area extends to  sq kilometers for more information please click on lrad dsxllrads compact highefficiency amplifier cabinet powers both systems and includes an ethernet based audio streaming device that supplies crystal clear live voice or prerecorded message transmission across a tcpip network the ethernet interface provides flexible communication and control for simple systems integration with ip enabled networks that modernizes mass notification installations and eliminates audio hissing and cracklingabout lrad corporationusing advanced technology and superior voice intelligibility lrad corporations proprietary long range acoustic devices® and revolutionary one voice® mass notification systems are designed to enable users to safely hail and warn inform and direct prevent misunderstandings determine intent establish large safety zones resolve uncertain situations and save lives lrad systems are in service in more than  countries around the world in diverse application